data.meta_site_name: For the Next-Gen of Telugu Cinema
data.text:
Renowned director B Narsing Rao’s films are being screened in Hyderabad from May 4th to May 10th, Unfortunately his most critically acclaimed film Daasi was screened today. Daasi had won 5 National awards in 1988.

Maa Ooru which also won National Award is to be screened on 10th May. For parallel cinema lovers who do not want to waste their money on the new releases, this is a great way to watch the works of B Narsing Rao. Do not miss it at any cost!

The remaining schedule is given below and the tickets can be purchased on http://www.fullhyderabad.com

Matti Manushulu – 7th May 7:00 PM

Harivillu – 8th May 7:00 PM

The City – 9th May 7:00 PM

Maa Ooru – 10th May 7:00 PM

Aakruthi – 10th May 7:00 PM

All movies are being screened at Lamakaan, Banjara Hills(In The Lane Adjacent To CBay, Opposite GVK One, Road No 1, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad – 500034)
